{
  "abstract": "Of 25 soyabean genotypes evaluated for resistance to budblight (TRSV) [tobacco ringspot nepovirus], Macrophomina phaseolina and Xanthomonas campestris var. sojens in field trials at Raichur, India, during 1991-92, PK 471, PK 472 and MACS 63 were the only genotypes to demonstrate resistance or moderate resistance to all 3 diseases",
